<plot>A successful lawyer, Marios, and his wife, Margarita, live in Athens, leading a quiet and rather conventional life according to established, average, middle-class standards. The husband has a love affair with a young lawyer, and the wife has her own adventure. The settled life of the couple radically changes, however, when the husband finds out he is a carrier of AIDS, and suddenly everything collapses: family, social relations, career.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?253492</url></doc>
